{"tid":1606243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 幫 手 推 ] [ 統 一 行 動 ] 十 一 港 殤 各 區 集 會 任 務","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T02:00:50.000Z","uid":59693,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d9a9562faed3193e84d47ba58584b5aeb8e7cb79","tid":1606243,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:43:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">TLDR</span><br />\n為免今次行動都只係集會開始，暴力衝突結束，而缺乏明確成果/目標。我整合左以下嘅各區任務同目的，方便十一活動係目標導向，減少死守及被捕。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">任務一. 突擊政權核心 撒下港共象徵物<br />\n任務二. 七彩繽紛賀國殤<br />\n任務三. 國殤七彩潑水節</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>任務一. 突擊政權核心 撒下港共象徵物</strong><br />\n內容. 突擊六區各政府合署/辦事處，換走納綷共旗/極權港共旗，同時<span style=\"color: gold;\">升上港殤旗，升旗時唱願榮光歸香港</span><br />\n目的. 表達對呢個納綷共國同港共政權嘅不滿，<span style=\"color: orange;\">拍低升旗片，再係twitter Tag任何外媒</span><br />\n準備. Anti-Chinazi 旗、黑港旗、口號旗、其他，手機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQUMHPX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQUMHPX.jpg&h=ab357ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>任務二. 七彩繽紛賀國殤</strong><br />\n內容. 又係突擊六區各政府合署/辦事處，見到有任何政府象徵，即刻<span style=\"color: gold;\">送上顏料、雞蛋、噴漆、墨汁等等彩色汁液</span>，賀一賀七十大壽，年年無今日<br />\n目的. 納綷共國最要面，見咁繽紛一定開心到跳起身<br />\n準備. 雞蛋六隻、小學雞書法墨汁、氣球、水彩、水桶、噴漆、油漆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hMwOV9V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhMwOV9V.jpg&h=a0282b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>任務三. 國殤七彩潑水節</strong><br />\n內容. 夏天未完，好熱，人地玩<span style=\"color: gold;\">水炮車</span>，我地可以加入呢個派對，面對任何熱愛納綷共國嘅市民、走狗、納綷軍，不妨參考泰國<span style=\"color: orange;\">潑水節</span>，加入<span style=\"color: gold;\">七彩元素</span>，你我大眾更開心。<br />\n目的. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">有防毒面罩嘅納綷軍中彩都要除罩</span></strong></span>呀！<br />\n準備. 雞蛋六隻、小學雞書法墨汁、氣球、水彩、水桶、噴漆、油漆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwRSDoi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwRSDoi.jpg&h=be6fecbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d47caecbc0c1768ff40ac7e4e702bb6f4c682c5b","tid":1606243,"uid":59693,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:44:23.000Z","msg":"求推 1/N<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aeac4577b2799e50f50045c815cd1541ea427bd","tid":1606243,"uid":80139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:44:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f869954737f646ce769da3727c7ed4662a32a4","tid":1606243,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:45:43.000Z","msg":"求推 2/N<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa3d5ae26f23e73c10c089b2c964f52f90b3240","tid":1606243,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:48:43.000Z","msg":"求推 3/N<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff456bb06d71d3bdc784e51736a22f470a40f9c3","tid":1606243,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb0ea1ad42239d4bae613a84849209392fbf6d0","tid":1606243,"uid":216992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"7彩講咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日一定要見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d73a749fc35bbf46d67efa6f770ef06e6c8f3a02","tid":1606243,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:50:38.000Z","msg