"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:22:43.000Z","msg":"一千連都係咁推架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7c989040d0413d042ef485c6019fab6167a258f","tid":1606243,"uid":8899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34W3LhF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34W3LhF.png&h=4df0cb76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4E5ea0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4E5ea0.jpg&h=13c529ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f46f7173193cdbf181a637b5f876a1986beea89","tid":1606243,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:25:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日出去前睇左先</span></span><br />\n來自CSD職員既提醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你班勇武手足,同我聽住,有部份前線手足認識我地,之前幾場戰役我地合作過,最初有人以為我地係鬼,詳細唔多講,我地係一班受過專業防暴訓練懲教署職員,之前已經係現場教過大家,如何組織防線同攻擊防暴,之前都有唔少進步,但今日我地冇出現,你地表現太差,中要咁多比人拉,我好心痛..<br />\n我地人手有限,身份問題,冇可能次次出現,我係度比些少資訊大家,希望大家務必share同發輝得好D<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.速龍都係人,佢地咩住咁重裝備同蒙面先至令信心大增,但大家留意下佢地人手一定唔夠手足多,只要大家穩固防線,只要佢地一跑出嚟,手足唔走向前攻,先用人火同磚頭攻,再快速向前推進, 趁機會足幾個差人抬去自己方向,呢個時候繼續用磚頭攻擊,同時向差人方向口射洗潔精地下,務別令佢地仆街,最重要立即除佢哋面具,之後私了..佢地以後就會驚..</span></span><br />\n2.佩槍唔係向上蚊,而係向內45度角向前推,大家明點做😁<br />\n3.如果執到警槍,同佢地玩過遊戲,逐粒子彈唔小心跌落坑渠,洗手間,包保玩殘佢地...<br />\n4.咁黑仔有狗用槍指你,可行情況試下用1秒用長竹,或雨傘打佢手同向上..<br />\n5如果打狗,唔該搵手足集中打腳,上半身有盾牌你打係冇用,要傷腳同關節先有足,以上除左增強攻擊同防護能力之外,就係要令到狗驚,你要記住佢地都係人,唔係超人...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.哨兵必須去遠少少,手足唔好集足一個地方,必須快速移動,不停向唔同地方攻擊,切斷差人增援,攻擊完立即走人,玩殘班狗..</span></span><br />\n7.盡量引班狗去橋下,用高空方式攻擊..<br />\n最後10.1見,大家努力<br />\n一班CSD職員上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G98aqhU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG98aqhU.jpg&h=91af3794&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ZJ5YCX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ZJ5YCX.jpg&h=73a5ecdc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44b54cbb81199184fdf23858c061d42d4470b324","tid":1606243,"uid":223029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:25:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e96d19b84dc777beb9e054de74e4e68a8ca304fa","tid":1606243,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f7b275d0b0bd6243b905ca1235095b61f59adaba","tid":1606243,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7c989040d0413d042ef485c6019fab6167a258f","tid":1606243,"uid":8899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/34W3LhF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F34W3LhF.png&h=4df0cb76&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4E5ea0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4E5ea0.jpg&h=13c529ac&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:26:49.000Z","msg":"攝衫要攝埋褲腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n防口腳位裝槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fef932df8f0a87ddcb1a1fe16de374524ae75d","tid":1606243,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:26:54.000Z","msg":"聽日見呀"},{"pid":"c3202e649991592fd5f4f538a94b0e92aa7d7fe1","tid":1606243,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e96d19b84dc777beb9e054de74e4e68a8ca304fa","tid":1606243,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:26:33.000Z","msg":"幫推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:29:52.000Z","msg":"唔該曬巴打<br />\n好多謝有份推post既巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c703368e2e78fad8f19d3ce9445a13da1511634","tid":1606243,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:31:52.000Z","msg":"出面太多post 我會努力推架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f32e2a8f8698de9c06955a0c1a4d3b3eda7d0c","tid":1606243,"uid":114550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:32:24.000Z","msg":"推呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84040285df49afc4ea4e63d3c6ce2949e8a73701","tid":1606243,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:35:00.000Z","msg":"衝突前有目標清左先, 唔係只係又係一日衝突<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[ 幫 手 推 ] [ 統 一 行 動 ] 十 一 港 殤 各 區 集 會 任 務<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/efHCLS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/efHCLS</a>"},{"pid":"52879d84b148138ab6882dab10bec0ebe287ebdd","tid":1606243,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:37:26.000Z","msg":"太多行動po<br />\n好事嚟<br />\n凡行動我都會推 唔洗多謝"},{"pid":"abe237aa7e75478e439b3b466d5db4e133dea128","tid":1606243,"uid":212843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:37:48.000Z","msg":"不過得幾丁友 推好密都係冇用"},{"pid":"4293aaff88382adcae3e8311a017a50d0f3b9f42","tid":1606243,"uid":237739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9a9562faed3193e84d47ba58584b5aeb8e7cb79","tid":1606243,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:43:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">TLDR</span><br />\n為免今次行動都只係集會開始，暴力衝突結束，而缺乏明確成果/目標。我整合左以下嘅各區任務同目的，方便十一活動係目標導向，減少死守及被捕。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">任務一. 突擊政權核心 撒下港共象徵物<br />\n任務二. 七彩繽紛賀國殤<br />\n任務三. 國殤七彩潑水節</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>任務一. 突擊政權核心 撒下港共象徵物</strong><br />\n內容. 突擊六區各政府合署/辦事處，換走納綷共旗/極權港共旗，同時<span style=\"color: gold;\">升上港殤旗，升旗時唱願榮光歸香港</span><br />\n目的. 表達對呢個納綷共國同港共政權嘅不滿，<span style=\"color: orange;\">拍低升旗片，再係twitter Tag任何外媒</span><br />\n準備. Anti-Chinazi 旗、黑港旗、口號旗、其他，手機<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQUMHPX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQUMHPX.jpg&h=ab357ecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>任務二. 七彩繽紛賀國殤</strong><br />\n內容. 又係突擊六區各政府合署/辦事處，見到有任何政府象徵，即刻<span style=\"color: gold;\">送上顏料、雞蛋、噴漆、墨汁等等彩色汁液</span>，賀一賀七十大壽，年年無今日<br />\n目的. 納綷共國最要面，見咁繽紛一定開心到跳起身<br />\n準備. 雞蛋六隻、小學雞書法墨汁、氣球、水彩、水桶、噴漆、油漆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hMwOV9V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhMwOV9V.jpg&h=a0282b87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>任務三. 國殤七彩潑水節</strong><br />\n內容. 夏天未完，好熱，人地玩<span style=\"color: gold;\">水炮車</span>，我地可以加入呢個派對，面對任何熱愛納綷共國嘅市民、走狗、納綷軍，不妨參考泰國<span style=\"color: orange;\">潑水節</span>，加入<span style=\"color: gold;\">七彩元素</span>，你我大眾更開心。<br />\n目的. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">有防毒面罩嘅納綷軍中彩都要除罩</span></strong></span>呀！<br />\n準備. 雞蛋六隻、小學雞書法墨汁、氣球、水彩、水桶、噴漆、油漆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RwRSDoi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRwRSDoi.jpg&h=be6fecbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"def874f1e73e31e7aa354cc7af656a3854a76d23","tid":1606243,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:37:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"266b35b8836371987935288cbf99a4dca73772d2","tid":1606243,"uid":250185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"29a56a2aa986ca41cd8855b4dc183325f496f967","tid":1606243,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"「TaiwanWarmPower」今晚（15日）在臉書發文，呼籲民眾一同連署「德國聯邦議會第95643號請願書」 ，支持「請求德國與中華民國（台灣）建立外交關係」，內文中指出迫害人權的中共不應代表民主自由的台灣。小編表示，可參考連署教學影片，2分鐘左右的時間就能完成簽署，如能在10月9日前達成5萬人連署，就有機會將此議題送進德國國會。<br />\n<br />\n#AntiChinazi<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2916703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2916703&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6i1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=70e1568b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2916703&h=2efc4681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2916703</a><br />\n<br />\n連署教學from TW:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/allen.taiwangermany/videos/pcb.2942668175748064/2942643702417178/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fallen.taiwangermany%2Fvideos%2Fpcb.2942668175748064%2F2942643702417178%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6i1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=58f9ba01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/allen.taiwangermany/videos/pcb.2942668175748064/2942643702417178/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n連署link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_05/_31/Petition_95643.mitzeichnen.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_05%2F_31%2FPetition_95643.mitzeichnen.html&d=Rx4KuutU7IQQNt32%2FBGh6i1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=bef5917c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_05/_31/Petition_95643.mitzeichnen.html</a><br />\n<br />\n大家幫下手, 聯台灣抗邪惡強国<br />\n<br />\n仲爭一萬"},{"pid":"41c86f48ea04b9419d3487461253617f56c4313d","tid":1606243,"uid":59693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"我唔想大家每次完都係比警民衝突搶走成果<br />\n外媒報導係最大既武器<br />\n但三個月都過左, 相類似報導只會愈來愈麻木<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以<br />\n衝